---
<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <div class="indexContent">
        <!-- <h2>你好！我是小满，一个数据分析师和编程爱好者！</h2> -->
        <p>
            Hello, I am a <strong>data analyst</strong> and a passionate enthusiast of <strong>designing and programming</strong>. I have a profound interest in data analysis and mining and enjoy solving practical problems using programming languages and data tools. I am proficient in several programming languages, including <strong>Python</strong>, <strong>TypeScript</strong>, <strong>Golang</strong>, <strong>Node.js</strong>, and <strong>SQL</strong>, and excel in using various data visualization tools such as Tableau and Power BI. Additionally, I possess a strong foundation in mathematics and statistics, enabling me to apply theoretical knowledge to solving real-world problems. I am highly enthusiastic about learning and exploring new technologies and aspire to continually enhance my skills and knowledge, ultimately becoming an outstanding <strong>data analyst</strong> and <strong>programmer</strong>."
